deals.title: Pure Green Acai Bowl
deals.itemDescription:
Base: acai, spirulina, banana, almond milk

Toppings: blueberries, sliced banana, hemp granola.

The Pure Green Acai Bowl is a blend of organic acai sourced from the amazon rainforest and blended with spirulina to give it a dark green color and a touch of banana for a creamy consistency. This bowl is topped with sliced bananas, blueberries and organic hemp granola.

deals.title: Pure Power Smoothie
deals.itemDescription:
Cauliflower, banana, almond butter, cinnamon, coconut butter, grass-fed whey protein and almond milk.

The Pure Power Smoothie is a healthy smoothie fueled by cauliflower. We combine cauliflower with almond butter, almond milk and grass-fed whey protein to create a truly unique superfood smoothie.

deals.title: Banana Nut Smoothie
deals.itemDescription:
Banana, cashew butter, grass-fed whey protein, coconut butter and almond milk.

The Banana Nut Smoothie is a crowd favorite with a taste profile that rivals a milkshake. It has a nutty flavor profile and richness from cashew butter paired with a dash of coconut butter.
